title: BBC2 Great Euro Crisis.avi
description:
I mainly upload programs from BBC1/2/4, which will only appeal to a small number of pirates.
 
I do most seeding overnight, so I have no way of knowing how many take downloads.
I have to depend on feedback to know whether I should continue uploading, and whether the quality of the uploads is good enough.
 
So please take a little time to leave some feedback. 
 
And please keep seeding !!
 
Winx HQ 1500/160k
